{"word":"ἀολλίζω","slug":"ἀολλίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀολλίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀολλής'><el>ἀολλής</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to gather together</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to come together, assemble</i>, <b>Il</b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of things, <i>to gather together, heap up</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}